OL,5,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FWith almost a fifth of fatal
OL,7,     Finjuries on UK's roads caused by
OL,8,     Fdrink driving, cops face pressure
OL,9,     Fto stop drivers under the
OL,10,     Finfluence. A biker is knocked off
OL,11,     Fhis bike by a drink driver.
OL,12,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FPaul takes the lead in a dangerous
OL,14,     Fhigh-speed pursuit through the
OL,15,     Fstreets of Stockton, and Spike
OL,16,     Fhunts down a suspect Skoda.
OL,17,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,18,     FJacko is hot on the heels of a
OL,19,     Fspeeding Mazda, while the
OL,20,     Finterceptors raid a cannabis farm.
OL,21,     FCanine cop Shadow sniffs out
OL,22,     Fstolen goods.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
